# Database & Operations

- Apply migrations in order: `001_additive_phase1.sql` → `002_phase4_iot.sql` → `003_phase6_production.sql`.
- Local MySQL (XAMPP): `/Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/bin/mysql -u root visual_inventory_db`.
- Daily backup: `scripts/backup/backup.sh` (30-day retention). Restore: `scripts/backup/restore.sh <file.sql.gz>`.
- Production stack: `docker compose -f docker-compose.production.yml up -d --build`.
- Dev infra only: `cd backend/docker && docker compose up -d mysql redis mosquitto`.
- Go-live checklist: `docs/GO_LIVE_CHECKLIST.md`. Recovery: `docs/RECOVERY.md`.
